quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,26,Futhi ngempela samdala umuntu ngobumba olomile olubhucukile oluqhamuka emhlabathini ecwelekile
  15,27,NamaJinn sawadala ngaphambilini ngamalangabi omlilo
  15,28,Futhi (khumbula) ngenkathi iNkosi yakho ithi ezingelosini ngempela mina ngingumdali womuntu ngobumba olomileyo ocubuzekile oluqhamuka emhlabathini ocwelekileyo
  15,29,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sengimenzile (u-Adam) ngaphefumulela umoya wami kuyena ngakho-ke ngathi yiwani nimkhothamele
  15,30,Ngakho-ke izingelosi zamkhothamela zonke
  15,31,Ngaphandle kuka-Iblis wenqaba ukuthi abe kanye nabakhothamayo
  15,32,"(UMvelinqangi) wathi, “Oh Iblis! kwenzenjani ngawe ukuthi ungabi kanye nabakhothamayo na?”"
  15,33,Wathi (u-Iblis) “angeke ngikwazi ukukhothamela umuntu owamdala ngobumba olucubuzekileyo oluphuma emhlabathini ocwelekileyo”
  15,34,Wathi (uMvelinqangi) phuma kulona (izulu) ngakho-ke ngempela wena ungogxoshiweyo (embusweni wezulu)
  15,35,Futhi ngempela phezu kwakho kunesiqalekiso kuze kube ilanga lokuvuka kwabafileyo.”
  15,36,"(U-Iblis) wathi, “Nkosi yami nginike ithuba kuze kube usuku lokuvuswa kwabafileyo”"
  15,37,Wathi (uMvelinqangi) ngempela wena ungomunye wabanikwe ithuba
  15,38,Kuze kube usuku lwesikhathi esiqokiwe
  15,39,"(U-Iblis) wathi, “Nkosi yami ngokuba ungidukisile ngempela ngizokwenza (ukona) kubukeke kukuhle kubona (abantu) emhlabeni futhi ngempela ngizobadukisa bonke.”"
  15,40,Ngaphandle kwezinceku zakho (eziholiwe) phakathi kwabo
  15,41,Wathi “lena indlela yami eqondile (elungileyo).”
  15,42,Ngempela ezincekwini zami awunagunya phezu kwazo ngaphandle kwalezo ezikulandelayo ezidukileyo
  15,43,Futhi ngempela isihogo siyisithembiso sabo bonke (labo abalandela u-Iblis)
  15,44,Sinamasango ayisikhombisa isango nesango lalawomasango kunengxenye (yezoni) ebekiwe (kulona)